          <formatted-text>
            <run fontalignment='0' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book'>Final Answer to the Business Question:</run>
            <run fontalignment='0'>Æ&#10;&#10;</run>
            <run fontalignment='0' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book'>Æ    </run>
            <run fontalignment='0' fontname='Benton Sans Book'> The dashboard shows that profitability is driven by product mix and logistics efficiency, while regional and inventory risks threaten stable performance. Strategic optimization will improve profit and reduce risk.</run>
            <run fontalignment='0'>Æ&#10;&#10;&#10;</run>
            <run fontalignment='0' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book'>Conclusion:</run>
            <run fontalignment='0'>Æ&#10;&#10;</run>
            <run fontalignment='0' fontcolor='#666666' fontname='Benton Sans Book'>     Revenue performance is strong, but profit stability depends on choosing the right products and shipping partners. A small set of products and logistics providers drive most profits, while geographic and inventory risks threaten consistency.</run>
            <run fontalignment='0'>Æ&#10;</run>
            <run fontalignment='0' fontcolor='#666666' fontname='Benton Sans Book'>Æ     </run>
