              <flipboard active-id='1' nav-type='caption' show-nav-arrows='true'>
                <story-points>
                  <story-point caption='Some regions show higher profit risk concentration, driven by inventory turnover, logistics issues, or margin pressure.&#10;These locations require closer monitoring, better inventory planning, and targeted risk mitigation strategies.&#10;Expanding in high-performing regions and stabilizing risky regions can balance growth and risk.' captured-sheet='🗺️ Profit Risk by Location ' id='1' />
