              <flipboard active-id='1' nav-type='caption' show-nav-arrows='true'>
                <story-points>
                  <story-point caption='Products in the top-right quadrant (high revenue, high margin) are the strongest performers and should be prioritized.&#10;Products with high revenue but low margin indicate pricing pressure or high costs.&#10;Low revenue &amp; low margin products may need repricing, cost reduction, or removal from the portfolio.' captured-sheet='🧭 Product Profitability Position (High vs Low Margin)' id='1' />
